Statements: Whenever we have to make decisions

condition
if that condition is true
   some action will be performed
if that condition is false
    some other action will be performed


If Charles is joining the class
    I will take the session
If Charles is not joining the class
    I will record the session for him to see it later

    =============================================

    1. If statement
        if(condition)
        {
           this will execute only if condition is true
        }

        if(charlesIsComing)
        {
            I will take the Session
        }